'''Donald A. Woods''' (born [[30 April|April 30]], [[1954]]) is a hacker and programmer. Together with [[Willie Crowther]], he wrote [[wikipedia:Colossal Cave Adventure|Colossal Cave Adventure]], a Text-Adventure strongly influenced by [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] on which [[Colossal Adventure]] was based.<ref>[http://www.faqs.org/faqs/tolkien/games/ FAQS, Tolkien Games] (retrieved 17 August 2010)</ref>

